\[\mathrm{I}(\mathcal{G},(Y,\bm{X}_{\bm{j}})|\circ)=\mathbb{E}_{\bm{x}_{\bm{j}}} \mathrm{I}(\mathcal{G},Y|\bm{x}_{\bm{j}},\circ)\] (6)

